text: Shukhov Lab (Named after the Russian engineer: "Vladimir Shukhov") is a international research and educational unit of the Vysokovsky Graduate School of Urbanism in Moscow open in 2017. the purpose of the lab was established in order to investigate the future of the cities in Russia and the rest of the world. == Other websites == * Shukhov Lab Category:Colleges and universities in Moscow Category:2017 establishments in Europe Category:2010s establishments in Russia
title: Shukhov Lab
